Package: nanolx-base
Architecture: all
Depends:
 nanolx-admin,
 nanolx-apt-tools,
 nanolx-apt-sources,
 nanolx-cli,
 nanolx-x11,
 nanolx-security,
 nanolx-net,
 nanolx-devel-cli,
 nanolx-devel-android,
 nanolx-devel-x11,
 nanolx-media-codecs,
 nanolx-media-cli,
 nanolx-media-x11,
 nanolx-games,
 nanolx-games-emu,
Recommends:
 nanolx-themes
Suggests:
 nanolx-citrix-config
Description: Nanolx base package
 Nanolx is a set of meta-packages, wich I use to aid in syncing the package
 selection between my machine and machines that are maintained by me.

