Description: Collection of emulators
 This meta-package installs a collection of emulators.
 .
 NOTE: only use self-made ROMs (using homebrew, hardware mods, or
       tools like Retrode). Downloading ROMs is often illegal. Known
       exceptions: ROMs where the copyright expired, ROMs distributed
       by the copyright holder (or it's legal successor) and Homebrew
       ROMs (completely self-made).

Package: nanolx-citrix-config
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
 ctxusb,
 icaclient,
 zoom,
 zoomvdi-universal-plugin,
 speex,
 v4l2loopback-dkms,
 pipewire-v4l2,
 libcamera-v4l2,
 bind9-dnsutils,
 pipewire-alsa,
 pipewire-pulse,
 llvm-libunwind1,
 gnome-keyring,
 rng-tools5
Replaces: icaclient
Description: Citrix Workspace Support package
 Additional integration and configuration for Citrix, as per
 AUR: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/icaclient
 .
 The Script nanolx-ctx in /usr/sbin may be used to enhance citrix experience
 .
 This package also depends on Zoom and the VDI-Plugin.

